description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Elon Musk's Twitter poll (https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1593767953706921985?s=20&t=5pjMK0_2Z-Efv2wykk7AJQ) on whether @realDonaldTrump should be reinstated has a greater percentage of "Yes" votes than "No" votes when it closes. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If there is an equal percentage of "Yes" and "No" votes when Musk's poll closes, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market will be the poll Elon Musk tweeted on his verified Twitter account @elonmusk (https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1593767953706921985?s=20&t=5pjMK0_2Z-Efv2wykk7AJQ), however credible reporting may also be used.

If this poll is deleted before it ends, this market will resolve to "No".
